
# VM 07 ‚Äì BlackMirror-Web (Vulnerable Webapp)

## üñ•Ô∏è VM Configuration
- **RAM:** 2 GB
- **vCPU:** 1
- **Disk:** 20 GB
- **OS:** Ubuntu Server 22.04 LTS
- **Network:**
  - Host-Only (VMnet2 - DMZ)
